                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6510" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1026</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8291 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破产重整，力帆科技再启航</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Bankruptcy reorganization, Lifan Technology set sail again</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石善冲，窦金鑫，赵志刚，何金</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">力帆科技(集团)股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破产重整；力帆科技；联合投资人；重整模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Bankruptcy Reorganization; Lifan Technology; Joint Investors; Reintegration Model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020年，“破产”成为汽车行业的年度关键词之一，许多车企被时代所淘汰，黯然离场。作为首家在A股上市的民营乘用车企业，力帆科技也陷入了破产边缘，被迫进行破产重整。然而，其却利用重整制度，创新采用“联合体”形式招募投资人并制定债务清偿方案，仅历时102天便顺利完成重整，回归新能源车企赛道。本案例以力帆科技破产重整事件为主线，叙述了其从风光上市到债务危机爆发，最后借助破产重整涅槃重生的全过程，重点从投资人选择及重整计划制定两方面分析力帆科技在短时间内顺利完成重整的原因。案例旨在引导学生思考破产重整的制度优势、进而思考重整投资人的选择和重整模式，并通过对比力帆科技与众泰的重整过程总结其成功的本质以及对同行的借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2020, &quot;bankruptcy&quot; became one of the annual key words of the automobile industry, and many automobile enterprises were eliminated by the times and left the market sadly. As the first private passenger car enterprise listed on a shares, Lifan technology also fell into the brink of bankruptcy and was forced to bankruptcy reorganization. However, it used the restructuring system, innovatively adopted the form of &quot;Consortium&quot; to recruit investors and formulate a debt repayment plan. It took only 102 days to successfully complete the restructuring and return to the track of new energy vehicle enterprises. This case takes Lifan technology&#39;s bankruptcy and reorganization event as the main line, describes its whole process from listing to the outbreak of debt crisis, and finally analyzes the reasons for Lifan technology&#39;s successful reorganization in a short time from two aspects: Investor selection and reorganization plan formulation. The case aims to guide students to think about the institutional advantages of bankruptcy reorganization, and then think about the choice of reorganization investors and reorganization mode. By comparing the reorganization process of Lifan technology and Zhongtai, it summarizes the essence of its success and its reference significance to peers.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》、《高级财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略失效；破产程序；营运价值理论；重整投资人的选择依据及方式；破产重整樸式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
